title: GAME OF THRONES Season 8 Episode 5 New Photos, Clues, and Predictions!
author: Think Story
comment: I just hope someone smacks Jon for not giving a proper goodbye to Ghost

People are crying out to avenge Missandei and Rhaegal, while I'm still waiting for vengeance for my man Ned!!!  Cersei needs to die and so do the people of King's Landing.  The people of KL have arguably been the most vile characters on the show since it first aired.  The only good thing they ever did was throwing poop at Joffrey's head.
The amount of people mispronouncing Missandei's name makes me want to get hit with one of those magic anti-dragon spears.
Lena is doing such a great job playing Cersei
I think the surprised look from Euron will be something along the lines of Drogon wearing armor/ doubtful they would intro more dragons this late in the game
